commit message: Include current time in message when payment details are expired.
Extract constant for mime-type of private key backup.
Warn about loading private keys from strangers.
Hint at appending wallet dump when reporting an issue.
Remove auto-migration of long forgotten Java-serialized wallets.
Use the protobuf wallet format for automatic backups.
Move payment protocol related constants to respective class.
Remove address selector when requesting coins.
Promote usage of BIP70 in tap-to-pay payment requests.
Use fragment transaction rather than <fragment> in address book layout. This is an ugly workaround, but it fixes several issues regarding configuration changes.
